            "title": "天水圍栢慧豪園2房 443萬元成交  13年升值逾7成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14824368&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中原地產天水圍區域分行表示，栢慧豪園3月錄得12宗買賣成交，按月激增5倍。其中5座高層H室，實用面積494平方呎，兩房間隔，向東，業主趁單位租約完結沽貨止賺，開價468萬元，放盤不久獲買家洽購，減價25萬元，以443萬元沽出，實用呎價8968元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原業主於2012年4月以255萬元買人單位，持貨13年，未計租金收入，賬面獲利188萬元，升值73%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14824368-%e5%a4%a9%e6%b0%b4%e5%9c%8d%e6%a0%a2%e6%85%a7%e8%b1%aa%e5%9c%922%e6%88%bf-443%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-13%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%87%e5%80%bc%e9%80%be7%e6%88%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 15:10:54",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "交投重越萬億 滬指收跌8點 深指挫1.4% 家電股受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">市場繼續消化美國關稅消息，內地A股午後於低位橫行，滬深兩市成交重越萬億。主要板塊互有升跌，家電行業壓力較明顯。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/China_Supply_Chain_Expo_24332553928753.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/China_Supply_Chain_Expo_24332553928753.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開30點、跌至3319點即見半日低位，未幾跌幅已收窄一半，早市中段更曾不止一次倒升，最高見3358點，升8點，於早市後段開始「潛水」，午後在大致在跌20點以內波動；滬指最後收報3342點，跌8點或0.24%，成交4865.1億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指今日則全程報跌，高位10481點，亦跌31點，全日低位於午後做出，見10328點，跌185點；深指收報10365點，跌147點或1.4%，成交6511.1億元。滬深兩市成交合共11376.2億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌22點或0.59%，以3861點收市；創業板指數跌39點或1.86%，報2065點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：海信家電官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00921-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：海信家電官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250108_FI_source-web_00921-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：海信家電官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">家電行業沽壓較重，海信家電(00921)A股(000921.SZ)挫5.42%，報27.6元；海爾智家(06690)A股(600690.SH)跌3.04%，報26.2元；美的集團(00300)A股(000333.SZ)也跌3.42%，報73.36元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">白酒股明顯強勢，貴州茅台(600519.SH)昨晚公布2024年度業績，淨利潤按年升15.4%，又大派現金紅利，每10股派276.24元，計入已派的中期分紅，全年分紅額再創新高，並通過於2024年至2026年度分紅比率不於75%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"貴州茅台官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240513_FI_source-web_600519.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"貴州茅台官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240513_FI_source-web_600519.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">貴州茅台官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">貴州茅台今早低開後不久即轉升，收報1568.88元，升19.86元或1.28%。多隻白酒股均受捧，舍得酒業(600702.SH)升幅擴大至4.89%，古井貢酒(000596.SZ)、酒鬼酒(000799.SZ)、瀘州老窖(000568.SZ)、山西汾酒(600809.SH)等齊漲超過2%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14827839-%e4%ba%a4%e6%8a%95%e9%87%8d%e8%b6%8a%e8%90%ac%e5%84%84-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c8%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e6%8c%ab1-4-%e5%ae%b6%e9%9b%bb%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%97%e5%a3%93",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 15:10:47",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "乘聯分會：3月份全國乘用車新能源市場零售按年升39%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">乘聯分會發表最新統計數據，顯示3月份，全國乘用車新能源市場零售98.8萬輛，按年升39%，按月更增44%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250401_FI_source-ap_china-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250401_FI_source-ap_china-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今年以來，全國乘用車新能源市場累計零售241.4萬輛，按月提升37%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">至於全國乘用車市場零售方面，3月份錄得188.9萬輛，按年增12%，按月更升36%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14827793-%e4%b9%98%e8%81%af%e5%88%86%e6%9c%83%ef%bc%9a3%e6%9c%88%e4%bb%bd%e5%85%a8%e5%9c%8b%e4%b9%98%e7%94%a8%e8%bb%8a%e6%96%b0%e8%83%bd%e6%ba%90%e5%b8%82%e5%a0%b4%e9%9b%b6%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%873",
