            "pub_date": "2025-04-03 15:05:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "韓股失守2500點關口　低收約0.8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">韓股失守2500點關口，美國對多個國家及地區徵收對等關稅。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">南韓首爾綜合指數初段低見2437點，一度跌2.7%，收市跌幅收窄，報2486點，跌19點或0.76%，連跌兩日。</p>\n</div>",
